==Khennjo==

My ''real'' name is Kenneth Jo Deles. Most of my friends call me Khennjo or Ken - ''Kenneth Jo seems to be too cumbersome''.

I'm presently involved with the Adventist International Institute of Advanced Studies (AIIAS) Pathfinder club. As Deputy Director for the Teen Pathfinders, It's always a challenge to find quick and real answers for the various Honor requirements. The [http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Adventist_Youth_Honors_Answer_Book Adventist Youth Honors Answer Book]here at WikiBooks is very nifty and convenient tool for any Pathfinder! - Thanks to Jim Thomas for initiating this.

I am an Accountant by profession and but currently works as part of the team for technical accounting support. I love the outdoor, photography, cycling and stamp collecting.

I can be reached at khennjo@yahoo.com

