{{ Cluster | | name = [[w:Messier object|Messier]] 52 | image = | image = [[image:M52atlas.jpg|300px]] |caption=Credit: [[w:2MASS]]/[[w:NASA]]. | epoch = [[w:J2000]] | class = e | ra = 23<sup>h</sup>&nbsp;24.2<sup>m</sup> | dec = +61° 35&prime; | dist_ly = 5.0 [[w:light year|kly]] | dist_pc = | appmag_v = 5.0 | size_v = 13.0' | mass_kg = | mass_msol = - | radius_ly = - | v_hb = - | age = - | notes = - | names = M 52, NGC 7654 }}
'''Messier 52''' (also known as '''M 52''' or '''NGC 7654''') is an [[w:open cluster]] in the [[w:Cassiopeia constellation]]. It was discovered by [[w:Charles Messier]] in [[w:1774]]. M52 can be seen from [[w:Earth]] with [[w:binoculars]].
